ecmc Debian controller live image

This live image contains the ecmc controller installer.

For a real controller install, first install Debian 13 to disk using the
included installer. After booting the installed system, copy or clone
ecmc_debian and run:

  sudo ./scripts/install-controller.sh

For live-system experiments only, run:

  sudo ecmc-install-controller

The live-system path builds EtherLab for the live kernel and will not persist
unless the live environment has persistence configured.
